data.description: Welcome to this spacious ranch-style home with an inviting open floor plan, offering a seamless flow between living spaces. The large fenced yard boasts a charming patio, providing an ideal space for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. This well-maintained residence features a brand-new roof, updated bathrooms and fresh interior paint adds a bright and welcoming atmosphere. Situated in a highly desirable location, this property is conveniently close to Smyrna Village and the vibrant energy of the Atlanta Battery, providing easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Families will appreciate the proximity to top-rated schools, making this home an excellent choice for both comfort and education. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make this property your own! Schedule a showing today and experience the charm and convenience this home has to offer. Has a bonus room that can be used as a flex or 4th bedroom
